---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/ui/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/ui/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 9, 2026';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="Privacy Policy — AK Digital House"
      description="How AK Digital House collects, uses, and protects your personal information."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navigation />

    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <h1 class="page-hero-headline">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="page-hero-sub">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <div class="section-inner prose">

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>AK Digital House LLC ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website akdigitalhouse.com or engage with our services.</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact information</strong> — name, email address, phone number, provided through our contact form or strategy call bookings.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, time on site, browser type, IP address, collected via analytics tools.</li>
          <li><strong>Communications</strong> — messages you send us through email or our website forms.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide our services</li>
          <li>Send you relevant information about our services (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share data with trusted service providers (such as email platforms or analytics tools) solely to operate our business, under strict confidentiality agreements.</p>

        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can disable cookies through your browser settings at any time. Note that some features of the site may not function properly without cookies.</p>

        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes described in this policy, or as required by law.</p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@akdigitalhouse.com">contact@akdigitalhouse.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>8. Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes by updating the date at the top of this page.</p>

        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:<br />
        <strong>AK Digital House LLC</strong><br />
        Raleigh, North Carolina<br />
        <a href="mailto:contact@akdigitalhouse.com">contact@akdigitalhouse.com</a></p>

      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  body { margin: 0; font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", system-ui, sans-serif; color: #242729; background: #fff; }
  .section-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .page-hero { background: #F9F9F9; padding: 64px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .page-hero-headline { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); font-weight: 700; color: #1A1C1E; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 12px; }
  .page-hero-sub { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #999; margin: 0; }

  .legal-section { padding: 64px 24px 80px; }

  .prose h2 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1C1E; margin: 40px 0 12px; }
  .prose h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .prose ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .prose li { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .prose a { color: #D91E45; text-decoration: none; }
  .prose a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) { .legal-section { padding: 40px 16px 60px; } .page-hero { padding: 48px 16px; } }
</style>
